---

<section id="contact" class="py-20 px-6 border-t border-[color:var(--color-border)]">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-sm font-mono text-[color:var(--color-accent)] mb-3">/ contact</h2>
    <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold mb-3 max-w-2xl">
      Got a React Native project that needs a native-module specialist?
    </p>
    <p class="text-[color:var(--color-text-muted)] mb-10 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
      I take on a small number of clients each quarter so I can stay deeply
      involved. Email is the best way to reach me — describe the project in a
      couple of sentences and I'll reply within a working day.
    </p>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 max-w-2xl">
      <a
        href="mailto:sanathpetkar@gmail.com"
        class="group flex items-center justify-between p-5 rounded-lg border border-[color:var(--color-border)] bg-[color:var(--color-surface)] hover:border-[color:var(--color-accent)] transition-colors"
      >
        <div>
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-[color:var(--color-text-dim)] mb-1">
            email
          </div>
          <div class="font-medium">sanathpetkar@gmail.com</div>
        </div>
        <span class="text-[color:var(--color-text-muted)] group-hover:text-[color:var(--color-accent)] transition-colors">
          →
        </span>
      </a>

      <a
        href="https://github.com/petkarsanathraj"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="group flex items-center justify-between p-5 rounded-lg border border-[color:var(--color-border)] bg-[color:var(--color-surface)] hover:border-[color:var(--color-accent)] transition-colors"
      >
        <div>
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-[color:var(--color-text-dim)] mb-1">
            github
          </div>
          <div class="font-medium">@petkarsanathraj</div>
        </div>
        <span class="text-[color:var(--color-text-muted)] group-hover:text-[color:var(--color-accent)] transition-colors">
          →
        </span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
